324
00:21:58,100 --> 00:21:59,800
She can't be.

325
00:22:01,400 --> 00:22:03,600
- They sound happy.
- When I go to this kind of place later, I'll bring you.

326
00:22:09,200 --> 00:22:11,600
It sounds like only two people.

327
00:22:12,430 --> 00:22:14,910
Isn't it supposed to be a gathering for a group of friends?

328
00:22:16,000 --> 00:22:18,000
Interesting.

329
00:22:27,100 --> 00:22:30,300
Sorry for not knocking.

330
00:22:33,200 --> 00:22:35,000
So sorry for disturbing you.

331
00:23:03,400 --> 00:23:05,200
Let's go.

332
00:23:05,200 --> 00:23:07,000
My purse.

333
