399
00:27:11,000 --> 00:27:14,400
Sheng Zhening, are you trying to be noble here?

400
00:27:14,400 --> 00:27:17,400
Based on what I know, Evergreen is a mess right now.

401
00:27:17,400 --> 00:27:21,000
I wonder how long you will last.

402
