405
00:27:31,000 --> 00:27:33,300
Right, another thing,

406
00:27:33,300 --> 00:27:38,100
I need to correct you. Not every man likes to cheat.

407
00:27:45,800 --> 00:27:47,600
GM Sheng.

408
00:27:50,000 --> 00:27:51,800
Your key.

409
00:27:51,800 --> 00:27:55,600
Girl, eavesdropping is not good.

410
00:27:55,600 --> 00:27:59,500
GM Sheng was making a lot of sense, I was just learning.

411
00:28:00,400 --> 00:28:04,200
The way you are looking at me is not very appropriate.

412
00:28:05,600 --> 00:28:09,200
This is how I look at everyone. You are overthinking.

413
00:28:15,800 --> 00:28:17,000
I'm so tired.

414
00:28:17,000 --> 00:28:19,000
I told you not to go, but you just had to.

415
00:28:19,000 --> 00:28:22,200
That's right. Did you achieve anything?

416
00:28:22,200 --> 00:28:25,900
Han Chao is a jerk!

417
00:28:26,700 --> 00:28:30,200
He's messing around with another woman behind his wife's back.

418
00:28:30,200 --> 00:28:33,200
