434
00:29:47,500 --> 00:29:49,000
Yan...

435
00:29:50,400 --> 00:29:52,000
This way, please.

436
00:29:53,200 --> 00:29:54,900
Miss Xia!

437
00:29:57,200 --> 00:29:58,600
Ms. Yan?

438
00:29:58,600 --> 00:30:01,200
Right, I should call you Mrs. Han.

439
00:30:01,200 --> 00:30:02,600
Call me whatever you like.

440
00:30:02,600 --> 00:30:04,200
