447
00:30:21,000 --> 00:30:22,000
- Let's go.
- Okay.

448
00:30:22,000 --> 00:30:23,900
This way, please.

449
00:30:29,800 --> 00:30:31,300
Thank you.

450
00:30:37,400 --> 00:30:39,200
It's so comfortable.

451
00:30:47,800 --> 00:30:49,600
Mrs. Han.

452
00:30:56,400 --> 00:30:58,900
Your skin is so nice.

453
00:30:58,900 --> 00:31:02,200
It looks like getting treatments here does work.

454
00:31:03,000 --> 00:31:05,000
