503
00:34:44,050 --> 00:34:46,730
Knowing who he truly is, you still got married to him.

504
00:34:46,730 --> 00:34:49,150
Well, he begged me to, crying,

505
00:34:49,150 --> 00:34:52,170
saying that he would change. I don't know about that,

506
00:34:52,170 --> 00:34:56,860
