508
00:35:04,070 --> 00:35:07,180
We took this photo when we were in the Aegean.

509
00:35:07,180 --> 00:35:10,230
I heard that you like the Aegean a lot, too.

510
00:35:10,230 --> 00:35:12,810
Did he take you there?

511
00:35:13,670 --> 00:35:17,230
I don't think he will have any chance to take you on a trip anymore.

512
00:35:31,090 --> 00:35:32,490
Sheng Zhening!

513
00:35:32,490 --> 00:35:34,760
